  <h4 class="teaser-headline">
      <a href="/article/new-cern-course-teaches-particle-physics-basics-online?language_content_entity=und" rel="bookmark"><span>New CERN course teaches particle physics basics online</span>
</a>
  </h4> 
  <p>The 16-part course, currently in its pilot phase, is catered to high school students but available to anyone interested in learning about the fundamental questions in particle physics.<br>&nbsp;</p>

</article>
</div>
