  </div>




</a></div>
    
  <div class="teaser-date">12/17/24</div>
  <h4 class="teaser-headline">
      <a href="/article/inside-the-search-for-dark-matter?language_content_entity=und" rel="bookmark"><span>Inside the search for dark matter</span>
</a>
  </h4> 
  <p>About 30 years ago an "ideas guy" and a team builder joined forces to search for the invisible bulk of existence.</p>

